    <title>OLEC 富利源企業有限公司-水性接著劑、工業用膠、熱熔膠、包裝用膠:@ViewBag.Title</title>

    <!--[if lt IE 9]><script src="//ie7-js.googlecode.com/svn/version/2.1(beta4)/IE9.js"></script><![endif]-->
    <script src="~/Scripts/app/BrowerInfo.js"></script>
    <script>
        var gb_approot = '@Url.Content("~")';
    </script>
    <link rel="alternate" href="http://www.olecgroup.com/?lang=zh-TW" hreflang="zh-Hant">
    <link rel="alternate" href="http://www.olecgroup.com/?lang=en-US" hreflang="en">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/Content/css/swiper.css">
    @if (ViewBag.IsFirstPage) {
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/Content/css/index.css">
    } else {
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/Content/css/page.css">
    }
    @RenderSection("css", false)
</head>

<body class="@ViewBag.BodyClass">

<div id="wrapper">

    <section id="header">
        <div class="wrap">
            <h1 onclick="location.href='@Url.Content("~/index")'" title="回首頁">OLEC富利源企業有限公司</h1>
            <nav id="menu">
                <a href="~/index">HOME</a>
                <a href="~/AboutUs">公司簡介</a>
                <a href="~/Products">產品介紹</a>
                <a href="~/News">最新消息</a>
                <a href="~/ContactUs">聯絡我們</a>
            </nav>
            <nav class="top-nav">
                <a href="@Url.Action("index")?lang=zh-TW">::繁體中文</a>
                <a href="@Url.Action("index")?lang=en-US">::English</a>
            </nav>
        </div><!-- wrap //-->
        <div id="banner" class="swiper-container">
            <div class="swiper-wrapper">
            @if (ViewBag.IsFirstPage)
            {
                <li class="swiper-slide i1">banner 1</li>
                <li class="swiper-slide i2">banner 2</li>
                <li class="swiper-slide i3">banner 3</li>
            }
            else
            {
                <li class="swiper-slide i1">banner 1</li>
                <li class="swiper-slide i2">banner 2</li>
            }
            </div>
        </div><!-- banner //-->
    </section><!-- header //-->

    <main>
        @RenderBody()
    </main>

</div><!-- wrapper //-->

<section id="footer">
    <ul class="list-inline">
        <li>桃園市龍潭區高楊北路452巷28號</li>
